These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-1::.
6 different games are played: canasta, billiard, backgammon, poker, go, chess
The people use 6 different means of transport: scooter, ship, skateboard, snowmobile, taxi, tram
1. the person driving the scooter is the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing poker is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing go##1
4. the person driving the scooter is between the person driving the tram and the person driving the taxi##2
5. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
8. the person playing chess is the person driving the skateboard##1
9. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |     3      |  4   |     5      |    6    |
| Game         | go     | backgammon | canasta | poker | chess      | billiard |
| Transport   | snowmobile | taxi  | scooter    | tram | skateboard | ship    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: comedy, horror, mystery, satire, scientific, time-travel
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, tiparillo, davidoff, siglo, blend, chaman
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 2. the siglo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 4. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is the siglo-smoker##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 7. the davidoff-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the blend-smoker is in an even position##4
 9. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
10. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |      5      |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | satire  | scientific | horror   | time-travel | mystery |
| Cigar   | davidoff | blend | tiparillo    | chaman | bongani   | siglo   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-3::.
6 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, frog, rat, mouse, cat
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: basketball, cycling, golf, handball, ice-hockey, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
4. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
5. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
6. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person who's sport is handball is the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |    3    |       4       |     5      |    6     |
| Pet   | bird    | mouse | frog     | guinea-pig         | rat       | cat     |
| Sport         | basketball | golf  | cycling | weightlifting | ice-hockey | handball |

