.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-4::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, lemonade, 7up, juice, fanta
The people use 6 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, skateboard, train, tram, van
1. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the train is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the skateboard is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
7. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
9. the person driving the van is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | milk     | lemonade     | 7up | juice | fanta |
| Transport     | van    | motorbike | skateboard | train  | tram       | boat      |

