.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-6::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: hiking, cooking, dancing-climbing, collecting, dancing, card-games
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, british, polish, russian, spanish, turkish
 1. the british is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 2. the turkish is on the left of the polish##1
 3. the argentine is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 4. the person who's hobby is dancing-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is dancing-climbing is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is the russian##1
 9. the person who's hobby is dancing-climbing is on the far left or far right##3
10. the turkish is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6    |
| Hobby   | dancing-climbing   | dancing   | collecting    | card-games    | cooking  | hiking   |
| Nationality   | turkish | polish | russian | argentine | spanish | british |

