.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-7::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  analyst, engineer, nurse, project-manager, software-developer, writer
The people have 6 different hobbies: singing, hiking, skydiving, camping, woodworking, sudoku
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the writer##1
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the writer##3
 4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the writer##1
 6. the software-developer is on the right of the engineer##1
 7. the engineer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
 8. the nurse is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 9. the analyst is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2       |         3          |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| Job     | project-manager | engineer     | software-developer | analyst  | nurse     | writer |
| Hobby   | hiking         | woodworking | camping              | skydiving | singing | sudoku |

