.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-8::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, milk, sprite, tea, water
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: country, indie, reggae, punk, d&b, metal
 1. the fan of indie is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 3. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 4. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 6. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 7. the fan of d&b is in an odd position##4
 8. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
10. the fan of country is in an odd position##4
11. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
12. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |    3     |       4       |     5      |      6       |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | milk     | iced-tea | water         | tea        | sprite       |
| Music-Genre      | reggae       | punk | country  | metal | d&b | indie |

