3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
4. the person driving the ship is in an even position##4
5. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person driving the helicopter and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
8. the person driving the train is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |      4       |   5    |     6     |
| Transport   | train | helicopter       | tram     | ship     | snowmobile  | taxi    |
| Hobby      | puzzles | filmmaking | writing | magic-tricks | hiking | skydiving |

