 3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 4. the person drinking water is the alhambra-smoker##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 6. the old-henry-smoker is on the far right##1
 7. the old-henry-smoker is the person drinking cola##1
 8. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is the davidoff-smoker##1
10. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |       3       |   4   |     5     |    6    |
| Beverage    | almond-milk | lemonade | hot-chocolate | water | milk      | cola    |
| Cigar   | davidoff       | ritmeester      | chaman     | alhambra  | oliveros | old-henry |

